various meats in furnaces, with unique stages per meat type, and utilizes ArmorStands to display cooking stages and the meat being cooked.\\n\\n`initializeMeatStages()`: Initializes cooking stages for The class handles loading and saving player oxygen data, updating oxygen levels, and displaying oxygen information on the player\\u0027s sidebar.\\n\\n`PlayerOxygenManager`: Manages the oxygen levels pieces.\\n\\n`onPlayerDamage`: This function is an event handler that is called when a player takes damage. It checks the player\\u0027s equipped armor for the \\\"Talisman: Armor\\\" lore, calculates the total damage reduction, and applies it to the damage event.\\n\\n`hasReforgedArmorLore`: This function checks if an `ItemStack` has the \\\"Talisman: Armor\\\" lore in its item metadata.\\n\\nOverall, this file implements a damage reduction mechanic for players wearing armor with the \\\"Talisman: Armor\\\" lore, which can be used in a Minecraft server plugin.\",\"/src/main/java/goat/minecraft/minecraftnew/subsystems/music/MusicDiscManager.java\":\"This file is a Java class called `MusicDiscManager` that implements the `Listener` interface. The `Flight` class manages the flight perk for players\\u0027 pets in a Minecraft server.\\n\\n`Flight`: Manages the flight perk for players\\u0027 pets, including calculating the maximum flight distance, enabling and disabling flight, and displaying the player\\u0027s flight progress.\\n\\n`onPlayerMove`: Handles the player\\u0027s movement event, ensuring the player is in the correct game mode, resetting the daily flight stats if needed, and enabling or disabling the player\\u0027s flight based on the active pet\\u0027s perk and the remaining flight distance.\\n\\n`calculateMaxFlightDistance`: Calculates the maximum flight distance based on the player\\u0027s pet level.\\n\\n`enableFlight`: Enables the player\\u0027s flight and starts a task to drain the flight distance over time.\\n\\n`resetFlightStatsIfNewDay`: Resets the player\\u0027s daily flight stats if a new day has started.\\n\\n`disableFlight`: Disables the player\\u0027s flight and cancels the flight draining task.\\n\\n`displayFlightProgress`: Displays the player\\u0027s current flight progress in the action bar.\\n\\n`sendActionBar`: Sends a message to the player\\u0027s action bar.\",\"/src/main/java/goat/minecraft/minecraftnew/subsystems/pets/perks/WeakBonePlating.java\":\"`WeakBonePlating`: A class that implements the \\\"Weak Bone Plating\\\" perk for pets in a Minecraft plugin.\\n\\n`onPlayerDamage`: A function that listens for player damage events and applies a Resistance I effect to the player if they have the \\\"Weak Bone Plating\\\" perk active on their pet.\\n\\nThis file contains a single class, `WeakBonePlating`, which implements a perk for pets in a Minecraft plugin.
